===================
Django Yarr Changes
===================

Changelog
=========

0.1.2       2013-06-30
            Feature:    Added j/k shortcut keys

0.1.1       2013-06-30
            Bugfix:     When API URLs are not available, disable API

0.1.0       2013-06-29
            Feature:    Initial release


Roadmap
=======

Target
0.1.x       Views to manage subscriptions
            Display times according to user timezone, not server
            De-dupe multiple feeds with the same URL before checking
            Ajax mark all read
0.2.x       Improve render time
            Delay image loading
0.3.x       Feed categorisation and entry tags
            View by feed, sort by newest/oldest
0.4.x       List mode
0.5.x       Drop support for Django 1.3
            Introduce timezone support for Django 1.4 and later
1.0.0       Stable release, make available on PyPI
1.1.x       Adaptive feed check frequency, with smarter spacing to spread load

The roadmap is subject to change; if a lot of people let me know that something
is a priority, I will try to move it up the list.
